@startuml sequence_auth
title Séquence — Connexion (Sign In)

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #7C3AED
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #7C3AED
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #EDE7F6
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #7C3AED
skinparam sequenceActorBackgroundColor #F3E8FF
skinparam sequenceActorBorderColor #7C3AED
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFF9C4
skinparam NoteBorderColor #FBC02D

actor Utilisateur as User
participant "Frontend\n(Next.js)" as Front
participant "Backend\n(Fastify)" as Back
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

User -> Front : Email + mot de passe
Front -> Back : POST /api/auth/login
Back -> DB : Cherche l'utilisateur par email
DB --> Back : Utilisateur trouvé
Back -> Back : Vérifie le mot de passe\n(bcrypt)

alt Mot de passe correct
  Back -> Back : Génère un token JWT
  Back --> Front : Cookie httpOnly (morph_token)
  Front -> Front : Redirige vers /
  Front --> User : ✅ Workspace affiché
else Mot de passe incorrect
  Back --> Front : 401 Unauthorized
  Front --> User : ❌ Message d'erreur
end

@enduml
